src.registry.duckdb_registry#

Overview of duckdb registry.

This module bundles duckdb registry logic for the kgfoundry stack. It groups related helpers so downstream packages can import a single cohesive namespace. Refer to the functions and classes below for implementation specifics.

Module Contents#

class src.registry.duckdb_registry.DuckDBRegistry(db_path)[source][source]#

Model the DuckDBRegistry.

Represent the duckdbregistry data structure used throughout the project. The class encapsulates behaviour behind a well-defined interface for collaborating components. Instances are typically created by factories or runtime orchestrators documented nearby.
